<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff; 
        }

        .dashboard-container {
            width: 400px;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff; 
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #007bff; 
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .description {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff; 
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3; 
        }

        .button i {
            margin-right: 8px; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dashboard-container">
        <h2>Project Dashboard</h2>
        <p class="description">
            Open-source development encourages collaboration and sharing of software projects. 
            It allows developers from all over the world to contribute to projects, enhancing functionality, 
            fixing bugs, and promoting innovation. Join the community by checking existing projects or 
            uploading your own!
        </p>
        <a href="/projects" class="button">
            <i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i> Check Projects
        </a>
        <a href="/upload" class="button">
            <i class="fas fa-upload"></i> Upload New Project
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
